instructions: Put the dinner plate on the table cloth
Put the dinner fork on the left side of the dinner plate
put the salad for on the left of the dinner fork
Put the dinner knife on the right side of the dinner plate
Put the salad knife on the right side of the dinner knife
Put the soup spoon on the right side of the salad knife
Put the water glass above the dinner knife
Put the wine glass to the right of the water glass
Put the other wine glass to the right of the wine glass
Put the coffee cup to the right of the soup spoon
Put the bread plate above the dinner and salad forks
Put the butter knife on the top part of the bread plate
Put the dessert fork on top of the dinner plate with the prongs facing the water glass
Put the dessert spoon on top of the dessert fork with the bowl part facing the bread plate
Place the napkin on top of the dinner plate, leaf side up
